          <li>Have Claude Code scaffold the Next.js app and wire up Supabase keys as environment variables — confirm together that secrets are <strong>never</strong> committed to GitHub</li>
          <li>First deploy: even a blank homepage live on a Vercel URL is a real milestone — it proves the whole pipeline works</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

